  <releases>
    <release version="v0.9.4.5" date="2023-03-12" type="stable">
      <description>
        <p>
          This is the first version of Syncthing-GTK maintained by a new team.
          Changes:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Port to Python3. Python2 is not supported anymore.</li>
          <li>Miscelaneous fixes about icons</li>
          <li>Miscelaneous fixes about app indicators on KDE, Gnome.</li>
          <li>Translation updates</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="v0.9.4.4" date="2019-08-04" type="stable">
      <description>
        <p>
          Changes:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Creating ~/.config/autostart with wrong permissions</li>
          <li>Correctly terminating Syncthing Daemon when terminated by signal</li>
          <li>Crash when adding new folder</li>
          <li>Displaying folders multiple times in device editor</li>
          <li>i3 detection</li>
          <li>Cosmetic receive-only folder fixes</li>
          <li>Windows: Bypassing proxy when connecting to Syncthing Daemon (thanks @TrueXakeP)</li>
